{
  "stem": "5255.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why would they take you to a hospital?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There wasn't hospitals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no hospital for prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Once you got sick, it's goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You said something to me about the men who had lost their wives and children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These are actually the people that didn't want to live any longer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They not only went to the-- in my camp, they went in-- in the mines and threw away the lamps, but they also were through the-- in the electric fences.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They jumped into the fence to be electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lots of people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And also, the routine, you wanted to know about the routine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm going to tell you about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to work eight hours in the coal mine, because there were three shifts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One shift prepares for the next shift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a routine that takes place in 24-hour segments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if you didn't-- if you didn't finish your job in eight hours, and you had, let's see, an hour or two to finish it, you stayed for an extra eight hours, until you get back to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you didn't have much sleep to catch up to, because you had to be up in your particular shift.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you had two different types of clothes, one to work in, and one to be in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, actually, there was a laundry, and you gave the dirty clothes, and you get a set of fresh ones every day.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you showered every day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was cold water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everybody had a bed, an individual bed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but in three stories-- three rows up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you had a bed for yourself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they had to give you a pretty good condition, because, otherwise, you wouldn't be able to work.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
